OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain but this
OL,6,Fbecoming light and patchy during the
OL,7,Fmorning. A few brighter spells
OL,8,Fpossible in the afternoon, allowing
OL,9,Fthe odd sharp shower to break out.
OL,10,FBecoming drier and brighter in the
OL,11,Fwest towards evening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with some showery rain
OL,14,Fin the east at first, this soon
OL,15,Fclearing east. Dry, bright at first in
OL,16,Fthe west, before further cloud and
OL,17,Frain spread east overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
