OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy throughout
OL,6,Fthe day as outbreaks of rain move
OL,7,Feast, these heavy at times. Becoming
OL,8,Flargely dry with bright spells later
OL,9,Fas the rain clears away.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Ffrom Monday to Wednesday, heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
